body_html:
Found this issue via this StackOverflow issue.

The issue still persists in https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/linux/cpu/tensorflow-0.11.0rc1-cp35-cp35m-linux_x86_64.whl

Also, the nightly builds return 404 (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow#installation). The last successful nightly build seems to work though (https://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-python35-linux-cpu/lastStableBuild/artifact/pip_test/whl/tensorflow-0.11.0rc0-cp35-cp35m-linux_x86_64.whl), but it is rc0?

Confused of what to use.
